n of lhe vessel, review of documentation and interviews, the Inspeclor will take nole of any apparent changes l0 vessel struclure, machinery; or equipment which have nol be noted in the PIQ or did not follow the MOC process_', 'The Inspector will also nole ay obviously deleclive slruclure, machinery or equiprent nol covered by any delect report In addilion, delects caused by an incidenl; Or in inslances where defects had caused an incident, would be noled t0 see if an investigation had taken place.', 'KPI 7.1.1 requires lhal lhere is a documenled procedure for managernent of change. The procedure addresses both permanent and temporary changes onboard and ashore. These may include installation of new equipment and modification of existing equipmenL', 'CP 25 "management analysis and review" FMAN.1 in VMAlforms Seafarers" Practical Guide to SIRE 2.0 Inspections 23 any During');
