onducled and documenled in accordance wilh Ihe BWMP and BWMC . Timnes and duralion ol ballast operalions will be verified. When ballast waler exchange operalions were conducled, records relaled t0 the plans and assessment of the sequenlial excharige of ballasl, which must iridlude lhe longiludinal and torsional slresses al each slage of the operation, must be properly documented and be within limits Draughts and trimn at ''slage of the operalion will be verilied When ballast water trealment or exchange had not been compleled in accordance with the BWMP due t0 daiage or defect lo the ballasl waler lrealrnent planl, records ol communications with the and Port State Authorities condilions placed on Ine vessel musl be complied wilh and properly documenled:', 'The Inspeclor will sight Ihe Dallast waler lrealmnierl plant l0 eslablish thal il is furiclional and lhere iS ro evidence of bypass which contravenes wilh the BWMP', 'KPI 6.2.3 requires thal comprehensive procedures cover all aspecls of ballasl-handling operalions, including ballast waler exchange ard ballast waler trealmenL', 'BWMP');
