ronic formal, all relevant personnel must have ready access [0 workslalion and have received adequale training t0 be familiar in accessing the SMS. In case of the bridge having procedures and instructions in electronic formal only; the back-up independent ineans ol power t0 lhe workslalion on lhe bridge musl be provided', '', 'KPI 1A.1.4 requires that procedures and instructions are easily accessible t0 personnel ad available at appropriale localions Sulficienl electronic or hard copies ol procedures and inslruclions are easily accessible L0 all personnel, including contraclors, al appropriale localions', 'CMS manuals CP');
