Inspection repository is ulilised by the vessel operator; whelher the most recent PSC inspeclion had been uploaded Documented evidence thal any deficiencies raised during the last PSC inspection had been rectified and closed oul wilh approval from shore management through either the non-conformily reporting system Or defecl reporling syslemn:', '', 'KPI 4.1.2 requires that a defect reporting system iS in place for each vessel within the fleet. 30 Seafarers'' Practical Guide to SIRE 2.0 Inspections 2.8). wvilll', '');
