review; lhe company procedure which delines lhe requirernent for Basic and Advanced Training for service on ships subject l0 lhe IGF Code; which may be in lhe form of training malrix The Inspector will review: A Basic Training Cerlificale for one engine room Raling: Two Advanced Training Cerlificales sampled from the Master, Chief Engineer and Engineer Oflicers. On exisling vessels, alternalive cerlification as required by the Flag Slale Ship-specific familiarisation records for lhe LNG or low-Ilashpoint fuel systern INTERTANKO has developed the "Onboard Familiarisation Checklist: Alternative Fuels" which is available on the INTERTANKO Website:', '', 'KPI 3.1.3 requires that procedures are in place t0 identify and manage mandatory training; including refresher braining, for all vessel personnel.', 'NIA');
