on; as appropriale, musl be available. Simple opera inslruclions with a block diagram showing lhe change-over procedures lor rerole sleering gear conlrol systerns ad sleering gear power unils must be perrnanenlly displayed on the navigalion bridge .', 'The steering control systerns should not be deleclive in any respecl', 'KPI 5.1.2 requires Ihal comprehensive procedures L0 ensure sale navigalion are in place. These procedures may include actions upon equipment (ailure and supporling checklists:', 'automatic steering NPM 6.15 & 4.3.4.5.2 Auto-Pilot track steering NPM 6.17 hand steering NPM 6.15 & 4.3.4.5.3 Hand steering remote conning position steering NPM 6.15.2 non-follow up steering NPM 6.15.1 Changing between the steering modes available NPM 4.3.4.5.4 Changing mode of operation Limitations of and any restrictions imposed on any mode of steering (speed, rudder limit, location etc) NPM 4.3.3 Bridge watch levels table in page 164 defines the location of helm');
