, rinirum 12 hours before being overwrillen; If inslalled afler July 2014, minirur of 720 hours belore overwnlien;', 'The VDRIS-VDR muSL not be defeclive in any respec', 'KPI 5.2.3 requires lhal lhe person(s) responsible (or navigalional slandards ensures lhal navigalional procedures are regularly reviewed and updaled: The procedures are updaled l0 rellect new legislalion, lechnology and updaled induslry slandards. Examples may include ECDIS ad VDR including dala recovery:', 'The VDRIS-VDR is subject to an annual performance test an approved testing or servicing facility- PMS The VDRIS-VDR is tested as per maker''s instruction after any upgrade, maintenance or repair of the VDRIS-VDR itself- PMS The VDRIS-VDR is tested as per makers instruction after any upgrade, maintenance or repair of navigational or communications equipment providing data feeds NPM 6.24.1 Instructions are posted near to the VDRIS-VDR controls for preserving data to prevent it overwritten. NPM 6.21 VDR backup The circumstances in which VDR/S-VDR data is to be preserved t0 capture any data that may be of value to incident investigation irrespective of whether the incident related to navigational situations Shipboard contingency plan chapter 6.');
