prrienl is under repair/service, lhis musl be discussed al lhe pre-transfer conference ard & sale syslem ol work agreed:', 'KPI 6.2.1 requires that comprehensive procedures for planning cargo, ballast and bunkering operations are place for all lypes of vessel within Ihe fleel: The plarining procedure is specilic t0 lhe vessel lype and cargo lo be carried. This mnay include ship/shore interface and communicalions;', 'TSM chapter 4.16 Current electricity TSM chapter 6.5.3 Electrical equipment and appliances');
